I"ø<h3 id="freshman21">Freshman21</h3>

<p>Freshman21 is a Jekyll blog theme, base on theme
<a href="http://github.com/yulijia/freshman">Freshman</a>.</p>

<p>A tribute to WordPress Theme Twenty-Twelve and Twenty-eleven.</p>

<p>Enjoy.</p>

<p><img src="http://i.imgur.com/oSp7kacl.png" alt="Screen" /></p>

<h3 id="a-summary-of-features">A Summary of Features</h3>

<ul>
  <li>Provide single column and two columns layout</li>
  <li>Powerful configure file</li>
  <li>Comments by Disqus</li>
  <li>Support LaTeX (by MathJax)</li>
  <li>Syntax highlighting</li>
</ul>

<h3 id="demo">Demo</h3>

<p>Single column, please see <a href="http://yulijia.net/en/">my own blog</a>
Two columns, please see the <a href="http://yulijia.net/freshman21/">theme website</a></p>
